            </Button>

            <Label
            HorizontalTextAlignment="Start"
            FontSize="36"
            FontFamily="Helvetica"
            Margin="0, 20, 0, 20">Learn More About Us</Label>

            <Label
                FontSize="18"
                FontFamily="Helvetica"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">Stories &amp; News
            </Label>

            <Label
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start"
                MaximumWidthRequest="600"
                HorizontalOptions="Start"
                Margin="0, 20, 0, 20">Behind every cup of coffee is a story. Enjoy some of our favorites along with all the latest news from the storytellers at Starbucks Stories.
            </Label>

