            </Label>

            <Label
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start"
                MaximumWidthRequest="600"
                HorizontalOptions="Start"
                Margin="0, 20, 0, 20">Read a brief history of Starbucks, from 1971 through today.
            </Label>

            <Button
                CornerRadius="22"
                BorderWidth="3"
